SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772129063
OL,3,CPeople urged to stay out of River
OL,4,CItchen to protect endangered Atlantic
OL,5,Csalmon
OL,7,FPeople are being urged by conservation
OL,8,Fexperts to stay out of the River
OL,9,FItchen in Hampshire to help protect
OL,10,Fendangered Atlantic salmon.
OL,12,FHampshire and Isle of Wight Wildlife
OL,13,FTrust is among environmental
OL,14,Forganisations who are encouraging
OL,15,Fpeople to help protect the fish eggs.
OL,17,FThe Trust said the spawn is currently
OL,18,Fburied in fragile gravel nests known
OL,19,Fas redds which can be easily damaged
OL,20,Fand difficult to spot.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
