OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772129063
OL,3,CPeople urged to stay out of River
OL,4,CItchen to protect endangered Atlantic
OL,5,Csalmon
OL,7,FThe redd is a shallow depression in
OL,8,Fthe riverbed dug by a female salmon
OL,9,Fwho lays her eggs and covers them with
OL,10,Fmore gravel for protection.
OL,12,FThe eggs will remain hidden in the
OL,13,Fgravel throughout winter and will
OL,14,Fhatch in late spring.
OL,16,FThe eggs are particularly vulnerable
OL,17,Fand at risk from disturbance until May
OL,18,Ffrom activities such as wading, wild
OL,19,Fswimming, paddling and dogs entering
OL,20,Fthe water.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772129063
OL,3,CPeople urged to stay out of River
OL,4,CItchen to protect endangered Atlantic
OL,5,Csalmon
OL,7,FMartin De Retuerto, Director of Nature
OL,8,FRecovery at Hampshire and Isle of
OL,9,FWight Wildlife Trust, said: "Many
OL,10,Fpeople don't even realise redds are in
OL,11,Fthe river.
OL,13,F"They can be very difficult to see,
OL,14,Fand unless you know exactly what
OL,15,Fyou're looking for, it's all too easy
OL,16,Fto walk, paddle or swim right over
OL,17,Fthem - without knowing that beneath
OL,18,Fyour feet lie thousands of delicate
OL,19,FAtlantic salmon eggs.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772129063
OL,3,CPeople urged to stay out of River
OL,4,CItchen to protect endangered Atlantic
OL,5,Csalmon
OL,7,F"Any activity that involves standing
OL,8,Fon, walking through or disturbing
OL,9,Friver gravels - whether for
OL,10,Frecreation, dog walking, angling
OL,11,Faccess or river maintenance - can
OL,12,Fdamage redds and destroy the eggs
OL,13,Fduring the spawning season.
OL,15,F"People and dogs are being asked to
OL,16,Fkeep to the riverbanks and stay out of
OL,17,Fthe River Itchen from now until at
OL,18,Fleast May.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772129063
OL,3,CPeople urged to stay out of River
OL,4,CItchen to protect endangered Atlantic
OL,5,Csalmon
OL,7,F"This small change in behaviour could
OL,8,Fmake the difference between survival
OL,9,Fand further decline of this iconic
OL,10,Fspecies."
OL,12,FHampshire and Isle of Wight Wildlife
OL,13,FTrust says the River Itchen is one of
OL,14,Fsix chalk streams in England that
OL,15,Fsupports wild Atlantic salmon but
OL,16,Fnumbers have fallen because of various
OL,17,Ffactors including climate change.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
