PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772129063
OL,3,CPeople urged to stay out of River
OL,4,CItchen to protect endangered Atlantic
OL,5,Csalmon
OL,7,FIt added research has shown chalk
OL,8,Fstream salmon play a vital role in the
OL,9,Fecosystem by supporting insects, birds
OL,10,Fand mammals.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/6
